 <div class="container-fluid top-color">
			<h1 style="text-align: center; color: white;">Eligibility</h1>
			<hr style="height: 4px; width: 300px; background-color: white;">
</div>

</br></br>

<p style="text-indent: 50px;">
Some health conditions, medications, and travel locations may temporarily or
permanently prevent people from donating blood.
</p>

<p style="text-indent: 50px;">
Eligible donors are in good health, at least 17 years old, and weigh at least 115 pounds(>53Kg)
(for whole blood donations) or 110 pounds (for platelet donations).
</p>

</br>
<p style="color: rgba(77, 34, 39, 0.966);text-indent: 50px;">
<strong>Below are the most common eligibiity questions.</strong>
</p>


</br>


<!-- Medical conditions div tag-->
<h2 style="text-align:center;display: block; color:rgb(0, 62, 65);;font-size:30px;">MEDICAL CONDITIONS</h2>
<hr class="ruler">
<h5 style="color:rgb(4, 96, 99);font-size:22px;margin-left:80px;"><strong>Can I donate if:</strong></h5>

<div class="container-fluid container-color">
<div class="row" style=" width: 1100px;">
<div class="v">

  <!-- 1st question-->
  <div class="question" style="margin-top: 25px;">
    <h5 >
      I HAVE LEUKEMIA, LYMPHOMA OR ANOTHER HEMATOLOGICAL MALIGNANCY?
    </h5>
    <p>No ,You can not donate.</p>
  </div>


  <!-- 2nd question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I HAVE BASAL CELL CARCINOMA?
    </h5>
    <p> You can donate as early as one day after removal.</p>
  </div>
 
  <!-- 3 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I HAVE CANCER?
    </h5>
    If it has been more than 2 years since the end of your treatment, you may be able to donate.
    Please contact to doctor firstly.
  </div>

  <!-- 4 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I HAVE COLD OR FLU SYMPTOMS?
    </h5>
    Wait until you have felt well at least for one day.
  </div>
  
  <!-- 5 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I AM PREGNANT?
    </h5>
    You must wait until 6-weeks post-delivery.
  </div>

  <!-- 6 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I HAVE SYPHILIS OR GONORRHEA?
    </h5>
    You may donate 3 months later.
  </div>

  <!-- 7 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >      
     I HAVE AIDS/HIV? 
    </h5>
    Regrettably, you cannot donate.
  </div>

  <!-- 8 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I HAVE A LOW HEMOGLOBIN/HEMATOCRIT LEVEL?
    </h5>
    Wait one day for levels to rise.
  </div>

  
</div>
</div>    
</div>

</br></br>


<!-- Medical Procedures div tag-->
<h2 style="text-align:center;display: block; color:rgb(0, 62, 65);;font-size:30px;">MEDICAL PROCEDURES</h2>
<hr class="ruler">
<h5 style="color:rgb(4, 96, 99);font-size:22px;margin-left:80px;"><strong>Can I donate if:</strong></h5>

<div class="container-fluid ">
<div class="row" style="width: 1100px;">
<div class="v">

  <!-- 1st question-->
  <div class="question" style="margin-top: 25px;">
    <h5 >
      I HAVE A PACEMAKER OR IMPLANTED DEFIBRILLATOR?
    </h5>
    No, You cannot donate.
  </div>


  <!-- 2nd question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I HAD HEART SURGERY DUE TO HEART ATTACK? 
    </h5>
    You may be able to donate 12 months after a heart attack.
  </div>
 
  <!-- 3 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I HAD A COLONOSCOPY? 
    </h5>
    You may donate if you have had a recent colonoscopy.
  </div>

  <!-- 4 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I RECEIVED A BLOOD TRANSFUSION, SKIN GRAFT OR TISSUE TRANSPLANT? 
    </h5>
    You may donate 3 months later.
  </div>
  
  
</div>
</div>    
</div>

</br></br>


<!-- Medications div tag-->
<h2 style="text-align:center;display: block; color:rgb(0, 62, 65);;font-size:30px;">MEDICATIONS</h2>
<hr class="ruler">
<h5 style="color:rgb(4, 96, 99);font-size:22px;margin-left:80px;"><strong>Can I donate if:</strong></h5>

<div class="container-fluid container-color">
<div class="row" width: 1100px;>
<div class="v">

  <!-- 1st question-->
  <div class="question" style="margin-top: 25px;">
    <h5 >
      I AM ON ANTIBIOTICS FOR AN INFECTION?
      
    </h5>
    Wait until 1-day after completion and no signs or symptoms of infection remain.
      
  </div>


  <!-- 2nd question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I AM ON ASPIRIN, FELDENE, PIROXICAM OR ANY ASPIRIN-CONTAINING PRODUCT?
    </h5>
    There is no wait if you are donating whole blood. 
    A 48-hour wait for apheresis platelet donation.
  </div>
 
  <!-- 3 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I AM ON AN EXPERIMENTAL MEDICATION?

    </h5>
    You may donate 12-months after completion.

  </div>

</div>
</div>
</div>

</br></br>



<!-- Vaccinations  div tag-->
<h2 style="text-align:center;display: block; color:rgb(20, 62, 65);;font-size:30px;"> VACCINATIONS</h2>
<hr class="ruler">
<h5 style="color:rgb(4, 96, 99);font-size:22px;margin-left:80px;"><strong>Can I donate if:</strong></h5>

<div class="container-fluid ">
<div class="row" width: 1100px;>
<div class="v">

  <!-- 1st question-->
  <div class="question" style="margin-top: 25px;">
    <h5 >
      I JUST RECEIVED A FLU SHOT?

    </h5>
    Yes,You can donate.
  </div>


  <!-- 2nd question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I JUST RECEIVED THE HEPATITIS B VACCINATION?
    </h5>
     Wait two weeks.
    
  </div>
 
  <!-- 3 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I RECEIVED AN UNLICENSED VACCINE?
      
    </h5>
    Wait one year.
  </div>

  <!-- 4 question-->
  <div class="question">
    <h5 >
      I RECEIVED ANY OTHER VACCINATION?
    </h5>
    Consult To a doctor.
  </div>


</div>
</div>    
</div>

